    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/d60556a99e9e9a508658b5abbe06c57f.avif?t=1584938812\" width=383 height=92 /></span><br>Spend a day in a rainy castle and befriend, or fall for, a non-binary dragon.<br><br>Stars and Snowdrops is a short, atmospheric visual novel played from the perspective of Princess Kovida.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/2023f73c341acd6d6899a736adc1f144.avif?t=1584938812\" width=361 height=92 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/f86911a7072c5f3a2e0727097c0954eb.poster.avif?t=1584938812\" width=445 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/f86911a7072c5f3a2e0727097c0954eb.webm?t=1584938812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>This spoiled princess has a lot of growing to do in a very short amount of time, but ultimately her heart shines like the stars.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/e0965febfb27839d5c0d85e588b9f0d8.avif?t=1584938812\" width=600 height=252 /></span><br><br>The kingdom's royal adviser, Frel, who kelps Kovi along her path.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/ad600704e46f9cb9e80675df5d76968b.avif?t=1584938812\" width=600 height=252 /></span><br><br>A nobleman from the kingdom, Sahar has a few 'curious' ideals that he lives by.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/d1d5473a08f338dc51072acd75e540c7.avif?t=1584938812\" width=600 height=252 /></span><br><br>A guardswoman from the capital, Hatsu is as stoic as her armor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/ea10010bb869793467751d533ba3ba39.avif?t=1584938812\" width=361 height=92 /></span><br>- Three body sizes and skin tones for Princess Kovi for you to choose from. <br>- Gorgeous, animated backgrounds and characters.<br>- All characters are fully voiced by incredibly talented voice actors.<br>- A short, refreshing story with atmospheric ambiance, music and sound effects.<br>- Small conversation options that help dictate Kovi's personality.<br>- A very cute adviser~<br><br>Written by:<br>Riley S Keene<br><br>Featuring voices from:<br>Elsie Lovelock<br>Marissa Lenti<br>Duffy P Weber <br>Ashe Thurman<br><br><br><br>And original music from:<br>Johnathan Johnson",
